<H1><IMG SRC="earthani.gif" HSPACE=15 VSPACE=15 HEIGHT=64 WIDTH=64 ALIGN=ABSCENTER><FONT SIZE=+2>R</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>CIL
</FONT><B><FONT SIZE=+2>F</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>riday </FONT><FONT SIZE=+2>L</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>ecture
</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2>S</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>eries</FONT></B></H1>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

<UL>
<P><FONT SIZE=+2>O</FONT>ur lecture series takes place on Fridays during
term at 12.45 pm at the Research Centre. Due to limitations on space, advance
booking is advised for non-Cambridge residents. A light lunch is provided.</P>
</UL>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

<H2>Michaelmas Term 1996</H2>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

<H3><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=+2>1 October</FONT></FONT> </H3>

<UL>
<DT><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Autonomy</FONT></B></DT>

<DT><IMG SRC="ball.gif" HSPACE=5 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 ALIGN=ABSBOTTOM><B>Professor
Tom Frank</B>, <I>New York University School of Law</I></DT>
</UL>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

<H3><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=+2>18 October</FONT></FONT></H3>

<UL>
<DT><B><FONT SIZE=+1>Humanitarian Intervention: Enterprise or Entanglement?</FONT></B></DT>

<DT><IMG SRC="ball.gif" HSPACE=5 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 ALIGN=ABSBOTTOM><B>Professor
Chris Greenwood</B>, <I>London School of Economics</I></DT>
</UL>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

