<H1><IMG SRC="earthani.gif" HSPACE=15 VSPACE=15 HEIGHT=64 WIDTH=64 ALIGN=ABSCENTER><FONT SIZE=+2>R</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>CIL
</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2>P</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>UBLICATIONS</FONT></H1>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><FONT SIZE=+2>I</FONT>n affiliation with <A HREF="http://www.cup.cam.ac.uk/CUPhome.html">Cambridge
University Press</A>, the Research Centre has sponsored the publication
of such notable works as the Cambridge Studies in International and Comparative
Law series of monographs, the International Law Reports, the Cambridge
International Documents Series and many important monographs. In addition,
the Centre is developing a new collection of international environmental
law reports, to be launched in 1997. More information is available in the
current <A HREF="http://www.cup.cam.ac.uk/search/cat/cat.html">CUP catalogue</A>.</P>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

