<H1><IMG SRC="earthani.gif" HSPACE=15 VSPACE=15 HEIGHT=64 WIDTH=64 ALIGN=ABSCENTER><FONT SIZE=+2>R</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>CIL&nbsp;</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2>L</FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>INKS</FONT></H1>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><IMG SRC="constr.gif" HEIGHT=39 WIDTH=125 ALIGN=ABSCENTER></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+2>I</FONT>n the near future, we hope to provide useful connections
to sites of interest to international lawyers on the Internet: </P>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<UL>
<UL>
<LI>international law by topic</LI>

<LI>treaties and documents</LI>

<LI>international organisations</LI>

<LI>government agencies and regional organisations</LI>

<LI>non-governmental organisations</LI>

<LI>professional organisations </LI>

<LI>other academic institutions </LI>

<LI>periodicals and journals</LI>
</UL>
</UL>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><A HREF="mailto:eeh20@hermes.cam.ac.uk">The Editors</A> welcome suggestions
for additional links of interest to international lawyers.</P>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

