<TITLE>Law Journals --  subscription details etc</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<H1>Law Journals -- subscription details etc</H1>

<H2>This is a list of journal sites on the WWW which have no full text
content, or which make text available on a subscription-only basis. </H2>

<P>Typically they list contents of recent issues, subscription details.
Some also contain abstracts. </P>

<P>These sites typically remind their readers, with varying degrees of
tact, that if they want to see the full text they should either buy a copy
or subscribe to LEXIS.
<HR></P>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.duke.edu/journals/alr/mainpage.htm">Alaska
Law Review</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.uoknor.edu/departments/ailr.html">American
Indian Law Review</A> Subscription details. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.wcl.american.edu/pub/ilj/home.htm">American University 
Journal of International Law and Policy</A>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/anzjc/anzjc.htm">Australian
and New Zealand Journal of Criminology</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/abr/abr.htm">Australian
Bar Review</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/ajcl/ajcl.htm">Australian
Journal of Corporate Law</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/ajfl/ajfl.htm">Australian
Journal of Family Law</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/ajll/ajll.htm">Australian
Journal of Labour Law</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/aplj/aplj.htm">Australian
Property Law Journal</A> 
<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://ubmail.ubalt.edu/~ubiplj/">Baltimore University Intellectual
Property Journal</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.oup.co.uk/jnls/list/banklr/">Banking Law Reports</A>
Contents and abstracts </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.emory.edu/BDJ/bdjhome.htm">Bankruptcy Developments
Journal</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.baylor.edu/baylor/Departments/acad/law/lawreview.html">Baylor
Law Review </A>Contents and subscription information. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://web.bu.edu/LAW/publications/science_technology.html">Boston
University School of Law Journal of Science and Technology Law</A> Contents
and Abstracts. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.oup.co.uk/jnls/list/crimin/">British Journal of
Criminology</A> Subscription details and abstracts of recent issues. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://wings.buffalo.edu//law/blr/">Buffalo Law Review</A>

<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://law164.berkeley.edu/~clr/">California Law Review</A>
Current contents and abstracts. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.aber.ac.uk/~lawwww/cambrian.html">Cambrian Law
Review</A> Submission guidelines. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.juris.uqam.ca/rcds/INDEX_EN.HTM">Canadian Journal
of Law and Society</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://wings.buffalo.edu/law/circles/">CIRCLES: Buffalo Women's
Journal of Law and Social Policy</A> Journal details, and related links.
</LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://stripe.colorado.edu/~cjielp/Home.html">Colorado Journal
of International Environmental Law and Policy</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/cdrj/cdrj.htm">Commercial
Dispute Resolution Journal</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/cclj/cclj.htm">Competition
and Consumer Law Journal</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.construction-law.com">Construction Law Letter</A>
Subscription details and sample issues. 
<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.drake.edu/public/lawlib/index.html">Drake Journal
of Agriculture Law</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.duke.edu/journals/environ/del&pf.htm">Duke
Environmental Law and Policy Forum</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.duke.edu/journals/djcil/mainpage.htm">Duke
Journal of Comparative and International Law</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.duke.edu/journals/dlj/index.htm">Duke Law Journal</A>
Contents and abstracts. 
<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.berkeley.edu/~elq/">Ecology Law Quarterly</A>
Index, abstracts. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.emory.edu/ELJ/eljhome.htm">Emory Law Journal</A>
</LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.abanet.org/forums/entsports/e&sl.html">Entertainment
and Sports Lawyer </A>Bibliographies and Indices of past numbers. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.iue.it/AEL/ejiltoc.html">European Journal of International
Law</A> Contents, subscription details. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.iue.it/LAW/ELJ/">European Law Journal </A>Contents,
abstracts and submission details. From issue 1 (1995). </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.hull.ac.uk/Hull/Law_Web/journals/eplj/top.html">European
Public Law</A> Contents. 
<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://w3.law.flinders.edu.au/home/fjlr.htm">Flinders Journal
of Law Reform</A></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://nersp.nerdc.ufl.edu/~lawinfo/college/fjil.html">Florida
Journal of International Law</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://nersp.nerdc.ufl.edu/~lawinfo/college/lawrevie.html">Florida
Law Review</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.polaris.net/~flw/flw.htm">Florida Law Weekly</A>
Subscription information. Some information is available electronically,
but on a subscription-only basis. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.fdli.org/pubs/journal.html">Food and Drugs Law Journal
</A> Abstracts, index, subscription information</LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.fordhamiplj.com">Fordham Intellectual Property,
Media and Entertainment Law Journal</A> Submission guidelines, contents
of past issues. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.comlaw.utas.edu.au/law/foi/foi_rev.html">Freedom
of Information Review, Australia</A> Abstracts. 
<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://web.gmu.edu/departments/law/gmlr.html">George Mason
Law Review </A>Subscription details. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.gmu.edu/departments/law/gmucrlj.html">George Mason
University Civil Rights Law Journal</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.lawsch.uga.edu/~galawrev/">Georgia Law Review</A>
Contents. 
<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://studorg.law.harvard.edu/jolt/">Harvard Journal of Law
and Technology</A> Full table of contents and subscription details. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.uchastings.edu/pubs/hlj/index.html">Hastings Law 
Journal</A>  Index, abstracts.

<LI><A HREF="http://www.uchastings.edu/wnw/wnw.html">Hastings West-Northwest
