Journal of International Law</A> General description of the Journal. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.lawlib.uh.edu/publications/HLR/">Houston Law Review</A>
Contents, from Fall 1994 (Volume 31 Number 3). 
<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://muse.jhu.edu/press/tocs/ics.html">ICSID Review : Foreign
Investment Law Journal</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.fplc.edu/PROFIDEA.htm">IDEA : The Journal of Law
and Technology</A> Call for papers. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.oup.co.uk/indlaw/">Industrial Law Journal</A> Subscription
