<LI><A HREF="http://www.idg.fi.cnr.it/">Informatica e Diritto</A> Contents
of back issues. </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.butterworths.com.au/journals/ilj/ilj.htm">Insurance
Law Journal</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.oup.co.uk/reflaw/">International Journal of Refugee
