Law Journal</A> 
<HR></LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.webflight.org/scu-htlj.htm">Santa Clara Computer
and High Technology Law Journal</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.usc.edu/dept/SCLawReview/LR.html">South California 
