<DOCNO>WT18-B20-27</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000641-B007-104</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/RCIL/Sinclair.htm 131.111.173.8 19970122110345 text/html 4765
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
