<H1>Dedication</H1>
<PRE>
First, I would like thank all who have submitted information for this edition.  
Second, I would like to thank my Internet compatriots for their support and 
inspiration, including Peter Schmidt from Midnight Networks; Burgess Allison 
from the ABA; and Lisa Gregory (editor of <i>The Legal List</i>), Max Kelly, 
Al Servati, and Joanne Taylor from Lawyers Cooperative Publishing.  Third, I 
would like to thank my family, for their love and support, without which this 
book would never become a reality.

