1.1.16.  List Server - Listserv@VM.MARIST.EDU.

LISTSERV LISTS:
LISTSERV@VM.MARIST.EDU

REPUB-L (Republican Politics)

1.1.17.  List Server - Listserv@vm.ucs.UAlberta.CA.

LISTSERV LISTS:
