<H1>  Chapter 3.  State Governments</H1>
<PRE>
SHORT DESCRIPTION:
This chapter contains information about all US State Governments.  For state 
governments that do not have their own WWW home page, I have listed the page 
for that state from the W3 Consortium (http://www.w3.org).  An organization in 
this chapter would most likely have a domain name ending in .gov (government) 
or .us (United States).

One of the best ways to find the e-mail address for a particular individual is 
to call that individual.  If you choose to contact the individuals in this 
chapter via e-mail, please keep your e-mail message short and to-the-point.

3.01.  Alabama.

Domain:  None.
E-mail:  mailto:claxtond@asnmail.asc.edu
WWW:  http://alaweb.asc.edu

