<HEAD><TITLE>The Legal List - Law Schools</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<H1>  Chapter 4.  Law Schools</H1>
<PRE>
SHORT DESCRIPTION:
This chapter contains information about US law schools. All 176 ABA-approved 
law schools (from the ABA's 01/94 <i>A Review of Legal Education in the United 
States</i>) plus non-ABA approved law schools with an Internet presence are 
listed.  Each listing includes a notation of whether the school is public or 
private, and if it is not ABA-approved. For law schools that do not have a WWW 
home page, I have listed the page of that school's parent educational 
institution.  An organization in this chapter would most likely have a domain 
name ending in .edu (education).

One of the best ways to find the e-mail address for a particular individual is 
to call that individual.  If you choose to contact the individuals in this 
chapter via e-mail, please keep your e-mail message short and to-the-point.

4.001.  American University, Washington College of Law.

NAME AND ADDRESS:
American University
Washington College of Law
4400 Massachusetts Ave. NW
Washington, DC  20016-8084

SHORT DESCRIPTION:
Private.

Domain:  american.edu
