<H1>  Chapter 6.  Corporations Et Cetera</H1>
<PRE>
SHORT DESCRIPTION:
This chapter contains information about for-profit, nonprofit, and not-for-
profit corporations and organizations.  All <i>Fortune 500</i> publishers with 
a WWW presence are listed.  All major legal vendors (most of whom are members 
of the National Association of Legal Vendors) with a WWW presence are listed.  
This chapter also includes resources primarily made available by individuals 
rather than by an organizations, governments, or educational institutions.  An 
organization in this chapter would most likely have a domain name ending in 
.com (commercial) or .org (organization).

One of the best ways to find the e-mail address for a particular individual is 
to call that individual.  If you choose to contact the individuals in this 
chapter via e-mail, please keep your e-mail message short and to-the-point.

6.001.  ABA Journal.

NAME AND ADDRESS:
ABA Journal
American Bar Association
750 N.  Lake Short Dr.
Chicago, IL 60611

Domain:  None.
E-mail:  mailto:abajournal@attmail.com

