SHORT DESCRIPTION:
A research center within the Univ. of Nantes School of Law. Through its gopher 
site one can access an electronic law review "NEPTUNUS", texts of theses, 
French legislation, case comments and much more information.

Domain:  humana.univ-nantes.fr
E-mail:  mailto:thalassa@hermes.humana.univ-nantes.fr
WWW:  http://palissy.humana.univ-nantes.fr
Gopher:  gopher://palissy.humana.univ-nantes.fr

8.13.  Germany - Privacy Information.

