WWW:  http://www.rewi.hu-berlin.de/Datenschutz/

8.14.  Germany - University of Saarland.

SHORT DESCRIPTION:
The Gopher server contains the German Basic Law, the Civic Law Book 
(Buergerliche Gesetzbuch), Process Law (Zivilprozessordnung), and others.

The WWW server contains German and European codes, historical documents (e.g.  
Roman law), and the German WWW Virtual Law Library (law-related Internet 
information).

Domain:  uni-sb.de
WWW:  http://www.jura.uni-sb.de
Gopher:  gopher://pfsparc02.phil15.uni-sb.de

8.15.  New Zealand - Auckland University.

