FIREARMS-POLITICS@tut.cis.ohio-state.edu (list for discussion of
firearms legislation and general talk about rights and current trends
related to the Second Amendment of the U.S. Constitution)
     Send the following message to
     firearms-politics-request@tut.cis.ohio-state.edu:
     subscribe firearms-politics
     (also on majordomo@world.std.com)

FL-LIST (see FORENSIC-LINGUISTICS)

