LISTSERV@VM.TEMPLE.EDU or the Usenet newsgroup, bit.listserv.help-net,
is for beginning users of the Internet; the NETTRAIN list for people
who train others on how to use the Internet was started by Jim Milles
at Saint Louis University Law Library)
     Send the following message to listserv@ubvm.cc.buffalo.edu or
     listserv@ubvm.bitnet:
     subscribe nettrain Your Name

NETWATCHERS (a monthly cyberzine covering developments in the law of
