     Send the following message to listserv@nic.surfnet.nl:
     subscribe wob-l Your Name

WORKLAW@chicagokent.kentlaw.edu (discussion list for Labor Law;
subscription requests not automatic; need approval)
     Send the following message to listserv@chicagokent.kentlaw.edu:
     subscribe worklaw Your Name

WORLD LAW INDEX (index to Hispanic legislation worldwide/law of Spanish-
speaking/Latin American countries, plus Haiti, Portugal, Spain; 
Hispanic Law Index, in English)
     telnet://locis.loc.gov/

WORLDGOV@tomahawk.welch.jhu.edu (World Government; discussion of draft
treatise on world government)
     Send the following message to worldgov-request@tomahawk.welch.jhu.edu:
     subscribe youre-mailaddress

WPS-FORUM (electronic bulletin board for information re Worker
Protection Standard for Agricultural Pesticide)
     Send the following message to listproc@are.berkeley.edu:
     subscribe wps-forum Your Name

WSL@cc.wwu.edu (Washington Student Lobby Discussion list)
     Send the following message to listproc@cc.wwu.edu:
     subscribe WSL Your Name

XXANDLAW@law.wisc.edu (closed list for women law students)
     Send subscription request to Liza Kessler at ekessler@students.wisc.edu
     or owner-XXandLaw@law.wisc.edu

Y-RIGHTS@sjuvm.stjohns.edu (Kid/Teen Rights Discussion Group)
     Send the following message to listserv@sjuvm.stjohns.edu or
     listserv@sjuvm.bitnet:
     subscribe y-rights Your Name

YLOPEARL@listserv.syr.edu (Asian Pacific American Law Professors
Discussion Group; unrestricted list by and for Asian American law
professors)
     Send the following message to listserv@listserv.syr.edu:
     sub ylopearl@suvm.syr.edu [your name]
     (before 15 May 1995, was on listserv@suvm.syr.edu)


</PRE>
