<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000641-B012-72</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/SUBJECTS/1.HTM 131.111.173.8 19970122111813 text/html 13450
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
