<DOCNO>WT18-B20-91</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000641-B016-224</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/SUBJECTS/29.HTM 131.111.173.8 19970122113212 text/html 15369
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Wed, 22 Jan 1997 11:26:52 GMT
