<DOCNO>WT18-B20-104</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000641-B018-98</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/AUTHORS/K.HTM 131.111.173.8 19970122113833 text/html 18547
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
