<DOCNO>WT18-B20-116</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000643-B021-260</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/AUTHORS/W.HTM 131.111.173.8 19970122114346 text/html 13840
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Wed, 22 Jan 1997 11:41:09 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
Accept-Ranges: bytes
Last-Modified: Thu, 11 Apr 1996 18:32:46 GMT
