<DOCNO>WT18-B20-119</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000643-B021-354</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/AUTHORS/Z.HTM 131.111.173.8 19970122114501 text/html 2729
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
