<DOCNO>WT18-B20-125</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000643-B022-172</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/TITLES/F.HTM 131.111.173.8 19970122114738 text/html 10565
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
