<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/TITLES/H.HTM 131.111.173.8 19970122114845 text/html 7047
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Wed, 22 Jan 1997 11:46:10 GMT
