<DOCNO>WT18-B20-142</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA030-000643-B025-13</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.law.cam.ac.uk:80/TITLES/W.HTM 131.111.173.8 19970122115848 text/html 7883
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Wed, 22 Jan 1997 11:56:16 GMT
