 Enemy Within: Economic Marginalisation and its Impact on Crime Amongst Young Adults<p><li><b>Jason Moore</b><br>Socio-Legal and Historical Aspects of Homosexuality<p><li><b>Bronwyn Naylor</b> (Working away)<br>Representations of Criminal/Violent Women<p><li><b>Carolyn Newton</b><br>Working Cultures Amongst Prison Staff<p><li><b>Chester Oehme</b> (Working away)<br>Controlling Gang Activity: The Effect of Deterrence Principles in Suppression Programmes<p><li><b>James Oleson</b><br>Non-Serviam: An Analysis of the Gifted Offender<p><li><b>David Price</b><br>Security Categorisation and Allocation in English Prisons<p><li><b>Karen Ramoutar</b><br>Explanations of Frequent and Serious Offending<p><li><b>Susan Rex</b><br>Perceptions of Probation Orders in a Context of Just Deserts<p><li><b>Michael Rice</b><br>The Prevalence of Specific Cognitive Dysfunction Among Adult Male Prisoners<p><li><b>Karen Terry</b><br>An Evaluation of Sex Offender Treatment Programmes<p><li><b>Claire Valier</b><br>The History of Criminal Investigation and the Forensic Sciences 1790-1914<p><li><b>Alison Wakefield</b><br>Who Guards the Guards: Investigating an Unregulated Industry<p></ul><p><p><center><i>November 1996</i></center></p><HR><CENTER><A HREF="iochpg.htm">|Institute|</A> <A HREF="staff.htm">|Staff|</A><A HREF="courses1.htm">|Courses|</A> <A HREF="research.htm">|Research|</A><A HREF="libhpg.htm">|Library|</A> <A HREF="pubs.htm">|Publications|</A><A HREF="crimlink.htm">|Links|</A> <A HREF="http://www.cam.ac.uk/">|University|</A><A HREF="phd.htm#cdr">|Students|</A></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
