<HTML><BODY    BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><HEAD><title>Recent Research</title></HEAD><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="" SRC="cam2.gif"><IMG SRC="RES.GIF"  ALIGN=MIDDLE><CENTER><IMG SRC="BLUEBAR.GIF"></CENTER><br>The Institute is involved in a wide range of research projects.<br><A NAME="causes"><A NAME="theoretical"><H3>Causes and Development of Offending/Theoretical Criminology</H3><P><ul><li>	<A HREF="RESEARCH/A1&.HTM">Further Analyses of the Cambridge Study in Delinquent Development</A>  (Professor David Farrington with Professor Donald West)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/A2&.HTM">The Pittsburgh Youth Survey</A> (Professor David Farrington with Principal Investigator: Professor Rolf Loeber, University of Pittsburgh)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/A4&.HTM">Criminology and Beyond</A> (Dr Loraine Gelsthorpe with Prof. R Sparks of Keele University and Dr J Muncie and Dr E McLaughlin of the Open University)<P></ul><A NAME="crimeprev"><hr><H3>Crime Prevention</H3><ul><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/B2&.HTM">Inter-agency Aspects of Crime Prevention</A> (Dr Loraine Gelsthorpe and Mark Liddle)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/B4&.HTM">Closed Circuit Television in Public Places</A> (Dr Trevor Bennett and Dr Loraine Gelsthorpe with students of the Institute)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/B5&.HTM">Evaluation of Community Safety Strategy in Birmingham</A> (Mark Liddle, NACRO, with consultancy input from Professor Anthony Bottoms, on behalf of the Institute)<P><li> <A HREF="research/B6.htm"> An Evaluation of Burglary Prevention Strategies in Cambridge</A> (Dr Trevor Bennett with Linda Durie)<P><li> <A HREF="research/B7.htm"> An Evaluation of the Effect of Street Lighting in Crime and Fear of Crime</A> (Dr Kate Painter)<P><li> <A HREF="research/B8.htm"> An Investigation into the Effect of Environmental Cues on Offender Decision Making: The Case of Burglary and Vehicle Crime</A> (Dr Kate Painter)</P></ul><A NAME="policing"><hr><H3>Policing</H3><P><ul><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/C1&.HTM">An Evaluation of Area-Based Policing</A> (Dr Trevor Bennett)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/C2&.HTM">Offender Profiling</A> (Professor David Farrington with Sandra Lambert)<P></ul><A NAME="sentencing"><hr><H3>Sentencing and the Operation of the Courts and other Tribunals</H3><P><ul><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/D1&.HTM">Analysis of Sentencing Decisions of the Court of Appeal</A> (Criminal Division) (Dr David Thomas)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/D2&.HTM">Studies in the Philosophy of Punishment and Sentencing</A> (Professor Andrew von Hirsch)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/D3&.HTM">The Quality of Pre-sentence Reports</A> (Dr Loraine Gelsthorpe with Dr Peter Raynor, University of Wales, Swansea)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/D4&.HTM">Remand and Sentencing of Women Offenders in Magistrates' Courts: View from the Bench</A> (Dr Loraine Gelsthorpe)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/D5&.HTM">The Introduction, Operation and Service Provision of the Youth Court</A> (Kevin Haines and David O'Mahony, supervised by Professor Anthony Bottoms)<P></ul><A NAME="community"><hr><H3>Community Penalties</H3><P><ul><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/E1&.HTM">Study of the Effectiveness of Intermediate Treatment</A> (Professor Anthony Bottoms and others)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/E2&.HTM"> Policies and Practices Throughout the European Community which Act to Exclude Ex-Offenders from the Labour Market</A> (Dr Nancy Loucks in conjunction with NIACRO)<P></ul><A NAME="prisons"><hr><H3>Prisons</H3><P><ul><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/F1&.HTM">Control Problems in Long-Term Prisons</A> (Prof. Richard Sparks (Keele University), Will Hay (Plymouth University), and Professor Anthony Bottoms)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/F2&.HTM">Attempted Suicide in Male Prisons</A> (Dr Alison Liebling and Helen Krarup)<P><li><A HREF="RESEARCH/F3&.HTM"> Evaluation of Small Units in the Scottish Prison Service</A> (Dr Alison Liebling with Professor Keith Bottomley, Hull University and Dr Richard Sparks, Keele University)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/F4&.HTM">The Wolds Private Prison: An Analysis</A> (Professor Keith Bottomley and Mr Adrian James, Hull University, with Dr Alison Liebling)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/F6&.HTM">Vulnerability, Custody and Incentive-Based Regimes for Offenders</A> (Dr Alison Liebling, Economic and Social Research Council Post-Doctoral Fellowship)<P></ul><A NAME="mental"><hr><H3>Mentally Abnormal Offenders</H3><P><ul><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/G1&.HTM">The Supervision of Restricted Patients</A> (Mrs Susanne Dell and Dr Adrian Grounds)<P><li> <A HREF="RESEARCH/G2&.HTM">A Critical Review of Understandings of the Mentally Disordered Offender in the Penal System</A> (Dr Adrian Grounds)<P></ul><P><A NAME="victims"><HR><h3>Crime and Victimisation</H3></P><p><ul><li> <A HREF="research/h3.htm">The Nature and Extent of Domestic Violence in Cambridge</A> (Dr Loraine Gelsthorpe and Amanda Matravers)<P></ul><P><ul><li>  <A HREF="research/h1.htm">National Crime and Community Safety Survey in the Cayman Islands</A>  (Dr Kate Painter) </P><P><li> <A HREF="research/h2.htm"> An Investigation into Violence Within Marriage</A>  (Dr Kate Painter)</P><a name="drugs"></ul>

<HR><H3>Drugs</H3><P><ul><li> <A HREF="research/j1.htm">Drug Testing of Arrestees</A> (Dr Trevor Bennett with Stuart Lockhart)</P></ul><HR><CENTER><A HREF="iochpg.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="IoC Home Page" IMG SRC="f1.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="staff.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Staff" IMG SRC="f2.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="courses1.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Courses" IMG SRC="f3.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="students/student.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Student" IMG SRC="f4.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="research.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Research" IMG SRC="f5.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="pubs.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Publications" IMG SRC="f6.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="libhpg.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Library" IMG SRC="f7.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="crimlink.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Links" IMG SRC="f8.GIF" border=0></A></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
