he Penal Lexicon</A> - information on prisons in England and Wales.<p><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://www.open.gov.uk/home_off/prghome.htm">Police Research Group (Home Office)</A> - brief info.<p><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://www.le.ac.uk/CWIS/AD/PO/CP/cp.html">Scarman Centre for the Study of Public Order</A> - at Leicester University.<p><IMG SRC="blueball.gif"><A HREF="http://www.sosig.ac.uk/">Social Science Information Gateway</A> - meta-index.<p><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://www.smlawpub.co.uk/">Sweet &amp; Maxwell</A>  - legal publisher. Site includes court listings.<p><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://www.innotts.co.uk/~mick2me/mainpage.html">UK Police &amp; Forensic Web</A> - police links.<p></ul><HR><CENTER><H2><A NAME="European Resources">European Resources</A></H2></CENTER><CENTER><A HREF="#UK Resources">|UK Resources|</A>   <A HREF="#International Resources">|International Resources|</A></CENTER><ul><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://www.uni-hamburg.de/~kriminol/engwel.htm">Criminology at the University of Hamburg</A> - in Germany.<p><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://www.mpi-fg-koeln.mpg.de/">Max Planck Institute for the Study of Societies</A> - in Germany.<p><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://www.securidata.it/osscarc.htm">Observatory on Criminality in Italy</A> - crime statistics for Italy (in Italian).<p><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://www.sc.ehu.es/scrwwwjo/indexin.html">Onati Institute for the Sociology of Law</A> - in the Basque Country.<p><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://rvik.ismennt.is/~tho/NSfK.html">Scandinavian Research Council for Criminology</A> - research and links.<p></ul><HR><CENTER><H2><A NAME="International Resources">International Resources</A></H2></CENTER><CENTER><A HREF="#UK Resources">|UK Resources|</A> <A HREF="#European Resources"> |European Resources|</A></CENTER><ul><IMG SRC="BLUEBALL.GIF"><A HREF="http://apsa.org