<HTML><BODY  BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><HEAD><TITLE>COURSES AT THE INSTIT OF CRIMINOLOGY</TITLE><meta name="description" content="The Institute of Criminology, Cambridge, offers a number of courses of study, including a Master's Degree and a Doctoral programme."><meta name="keywords" content="post-graduate courses Master's Ph.D. M.Phil. graduate criminology law crime sociology psychiatry psychology police prisons philosophy theory punishment politicscriminologia criminologie Kriminologie"></HEAD><H2><IMG ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ALT="crest" SRC="CAM2.GIF" ><B> 
Graduate Courses, Admissions & Awards
 </B></H2><BODY><CENTER><IMG SRC="BLUEBAR.GIF"></CENTER><H2>Courses at the Institute of Criminology</H2><UL>
<LI><A HREF="MPHIL.HTM"><STRONG>M.Phil. Degree in Criminology</STRONG></A></p><LI><A HREF="PHD.HTM"><STRONG>Ph.D. Degree in Criminology</STRONG></A></p><LI><A HREF="mst.HTM"><STRONG>M.Stud. Degree Programme in Police Studies</STRONG></A></p><LI><A HREF="CROPINFO.HTM"><STRONG>Cropwood Fellowship Programme</STRONG></A></p>
</UL><BR><H2>Admission Procedures</H2><ul><p>The above courses have differing Admissions procedures. Candidates for <A HREF="ADDMI.HTM">admission to the MPhil and PhD courses</A> should follow the standard procedure for University Graduate Admissions, noting the Institute's particular requirements.</p><p> Candidates for the other courses should contact the Institute of Criminology for further details.</p></ul><BR><H2>Awards and Grants</H2><ul><p>Graduate students may be eligible for various <A HREF="awards.HTM">awards and studentships</A>. Students should also consult the University's <A HREF="http://www.cam.ac.uk/CambUniv/GSProspectus/index.html">Graduate Prospectus</A> for details of other awards for which they may be eligible to apply.</p></ul><HR><CENTER><A HREF="iochpg.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="IoC Home Page" IMG SRC="f1.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="staff.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Staff" IMG SRC="f2.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="courses1.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Courses" IMG SRC="f3.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="students/student.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Student" IMG SRC="f4.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="research.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Research" IMG SRC="f5.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="pubs.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Publications" IMG SRC="f6.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="libhpg.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Library" IMG SRC="f7.GIF" border=0></A><img src="fb.gif" border=0 align=middle><A HREF="crimlink.htm"><IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Links" IMG SRC="f8.GIF" border=0></A></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
