<HTML><BODY    BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><HEAD><TITLE>Recent Research</TITLE></HEAD><H1><IMG ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ALT="crest" SRC="CAM2.GIF" ><B>Recent Research</B></H1><BODY><CENTER><IMG SRC="BLUEBAR.GIF"></CENTER><H2>Research Project</H2><H3>An Evaluation of Burglary Prevention Strategies in Cambridge <BR>(Dr. Trevor Bennett with Linda Durie)</H3>	<P>The study aims to evaluate a selection of crime prevention strategies implemented by the Safer Cambridge Steering Group Domestic Burglary Task Force.  The work of the Task Force was divided into two stages.  The first stage involved collecting information on the nature of residential burglary in Cambridge.  The second stage involved implementing strategies based on the information collected in the first stage.  The programme will involve implementing strategies in one of the two main burglary hot spots in Cambridge and observing the effects of the intervention on victimisation and repeat victimisation.  The non-targeted hot spot will be used as a comparison area.</P><body><html>
</DOC>
