<HTML><BODY    BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><HEAD><TITLE>Recent Research</TITLE></HEAD><H1><IMG ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ALT="crest" SRC="CAM2.GIF" ><B>Recent Research</B></H1><BODY><CENTER><IMG SRC="BLUEBAR.GIF"></CENTER><H2>Research Project</H2><H3>An Evaluation of the Effect of Street Lighting on Crime and Fear of Crime  (Dr. Kate Painter)</H3><P>The study comprises a quasi-experimental evaluation of the effect of street lighting implemented in one-ward in the London Borough of Redbridge.  The evaluation involves conducting pre-test and post-test household surveys of residents living in the area scheduled for re-lighting and in a comparison area not scheduled for re-lighting.  The study will investigate the effects of re-lighting on public attitudes and on residents' perceptions of safety on the streets, as well as its effect on crime and victimisation.</P></body></html>
</DOC>
<DOC>
