<HTML><BODY    BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><HEAD><TITLE>Recent Research</TITLE></HEAD><H1><IMG ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ALT="crest" SRC="CAM2.GIF" ><B>Recent Research</B></H1><BODY><CENTER><IMG SRC="BLUEBAR.GIF"></CENTER><H2>Research Project</H2><H3>National Crime and Community Safety Survey in the Cayman Islands 	(Dr. Kate Painter)</H3><P>This study represents the first ever crime survey in the Cayman Islands and aims to identify levels of victimisation and fear.  The survey will be based on a national representative sample of the population and will ask respondents about victimisation and perceptions of safety.  It is hoped that the results of the survey will be used to develop crime and safety policies and programmes.</P></body></html>
</DOC>
