<HTML><BODY    BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><HEAD><TITLE>Recent Research</TITLE></HEAD><H1><IMG ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ALT="crest" SRC="CAM2.GIF" ><B>Recent Research</B></H1><BODY><CENTER><IMG SRC="BLUEBAR.GIF"></CENTER><H2>Research Project</H2><H3>An Investigation into Violence Within Marriage (Dr. Kate Painter)</H3><P>This study is currently under discussion with representatives of a prominent national television programme who hope to fund a survey of violence within marriage.  The study will explore the relationship between perpetrator and victim and the interaction between the two.  It is hoped that the results of the survey will be included in the programme to be scheduled on this subject.</P></body></html>
</DOC>
