<HTML><BODY    BGCOLOR="#ffffff"><HEAD><TITLE>Recent Research</TITLE></HEAD><H1><IMG ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ALT="crest" SRC="CAM2.GIF" ><B>Recent Research</B></H1><BODY><CENTER><IMG SRC="BLUEBAR.GIF"></CENTER><H2>Research Project</H2><H3>Drug Testing of Arrestees (Dr Trevor Bennett with Stuart Lockhart)</H3><P>The study comprises two pilot studies on the use of drugs among arrestees.  The first study is currently being conducted in the custody site of Parkside Police Station in Cambridge.  Arrestees are selected for interview by the reseacher in collaboration with the police and are asked about drug use and crime.  At the end of the interview they are asked to provide a urine specimen.  The sample is then sent to a forensic laboratory for drug testing.  The second study will involve conducting similar surveys in two police forces which will be repeated after an interval of one year.   The aim of the study is to determine the prevalence and the nature of drug use among current arrestees.</P></body></html>
</DOC>
