<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Main Page </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="image145.gif" WIDTH="315" HEIGHT="347" ALIGN=bottom
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><BR>
<BR>
The Texas Association of Secondary School Principals is a not-for-profit
organization serving the high school and middle level principals of Texas.
With 4,400 members, TASSP represents principals' concerns in many venues,
and plays an important role in statewide decisions regarding the education
of Texas youth. Committed to excellence, the association and its members
practice the motto.</CENTER>
<H2><CENTER><STRONG>&quot;Above all, students first!&quot;</STRONG></CENTER>
</H2>
<P><CENTER><BR>
<BR>
