<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Tech Lab Evaluation </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="image51.gif" WIDTH="392" HEIGHT="54" ALIGN=bottom 
NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"><IMG SRC="image238.gif" WIDTH="197" HEIGHT="44" ALIGN=
bottom NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></CENTER>
<H2><CENTER></CENTER>
</H2>
We would like you input on our conference technology labs.  Please take
a few moments to respond to the following questions.<BR>
<UL>
<LI>How advanced of a computer user are you?
<LI>Why did you come to the lab?
<LI>Were your goals met here?
<LI>Suggestions for future technology computer sessions?
<LI>What did you think of the TASSP Web site? Any suggestions?<BR>
<BR>
</UL>
<B>To reply please read the following instructions and click below.</B><BR>
<BR>
Under &quot;Subject&quot; please enter Mac lab, PC lab, or both depending
on the lab you used.  Then enter your comments and suggesstions in the space
provided.  You may also choose to provide your name.  To send your reply
press &quot;Post Message&quot;<BR>
<P><CENTER><A HREF="http://aus.computize.com/bulletin/tassp/postnew.html">REPLY<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
